            "title": "Regional Bank Issues May Lead to Consolidation, Says Charles Schwab's Sonders",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><div class=\"akcelo-wrapper akcelo-video media--169\" style=\"width:100%\"><div class=\"border:solid 1px #C0C0C0\" id=\"Zonebourse_Article_Video\" video-id=\"k63YqeYFZSdL3SE2Fp0\"><div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta content=\"Regional Bank Issues May Lead to Consolidation, Says Charles Schwab's Sonders\" itemprop=\"name\"/><meta content='Liz Ann Sonders, chief investment strategist at Charles Schwab (SCHW), examines strains in the regional banking sector and suggests that investors \"go up the quality spectrum\" to provide protection in portfolios.\n' itemprop=\"description\"/><meta content=\"2025-10-17T14:59:38+02:00\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/><meta content=\"/images/mtnewswires/A3478970.png\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/><meta content=\"https://geo.dailymotion.com/player/x80uo.html?video=k63YqeYFZSdL3SE2Fp0\" itemprop=\"embedUrl\"/></div></div></div>\n               Liz Ann Sonders, chief investment strategist at Charles Schwab (SCHW), examines strains in the regional banking sector and suggests that investors \"go up the quality spectrum\" to provide protection in portfolios.<p><span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTpvkfAwLuu\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'mtnewswires', '51373599');\">Bloomberg videos</span>, provided by MT Newswires</p></div>",
